  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb5\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u2018\u0b9f\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0ba9\u0bcd\u2019 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bcb\u0b95\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bae\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "\u2018Token\u2019 distribution of fuel begins in Nuwara Eliya",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "The island-wide distribution of fuel under the 'token' system has begun on the 27th.",
        "At two petrol stations in the main city of Nuwara Eliya, visitors are issued a 'token' of fuel registered by the military.",
        "When 6,600 liters of petrol arrived at the Nuwara Eliya Lanka IOC petrol station today (28) after a long hiatus, Nuwara Eliya Divisional Secretary Veeduna Sampath intervened to supply petrol to all vehicles at Rs. 2,000, three-wheelers at Rs. Decided to deliver on demand and is being distributed peacefully.",
        "It is noteworthy that the first token system has been introduced today with the help of the Army to reduce the fuel queue and the vehicle numbers are also being registered and the police are engaged in security duties for this purpose."
      ],
